# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback for provider pages.
#
# Per-provider HTML files don't ship with the deployment (22K JSONs in R2 +
# 22K HTMLs would exceed Cloudflare Pages' 20K file limit). The static
# export emits one shell at /hospital/_unavailable/ and one at
# /nursing-home/_unavailable/. These rewrites route every per-provider URL
# to its respective shell, where a client component reads the URL, extracts
# the CCN, fetches from R2, and renders.
#
# 200 = internal rewrite (URL stays, content served from shell)

/hospital/*  /hospital/_unavailable/index.html  200
/nursing-home/*  /nursing-home/_unavailable/index.html  200
